{"tid":245850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾聞 梁振英大灣區考察後趕回港修訂文件　重點修改：基本法47條立法原意","createTime":"2017-05-16T14:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T03:31:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd327bd8da78fcf54fdbd433741a0c189105d23","tid":245850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3975/ugl-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-3975/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E5%BE%8C%E8%B6%95%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%9547%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%8E%9F%E6%84%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F3975%2Fugl-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-3975%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%2580%2583%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25B6%2595%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2594%25B9%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%259547%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%2584%258F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=05914e11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3975/ugl-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-3975/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%80%83%E5%AF%9F%E5%BE%8C%E8%B6%95%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%9547%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%8E%9F%E6%84%8F</a><br />\n<br />\n眾聞<br />\n梁振英大灣區考察後趕回港修訂文件　重點修改：基本法47條立法原意<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 記者翁維愷 | 發佈日期: 16.05.17<br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英今早承認，親自為民建聯周浩鼎修改文件，建議修訂立法會調查他收取UGL款項的專責委員會研究範圍。文件紀錄顯示，梁振英是在4月21日晚上10時半修訂文件，當日他剛結束大灣區考察之旅，從珠海回到香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁振英4月19日帶隊到大灣區考察，直至21日才結束行程。政府新聞處圖片<br />\n梁振英自4月19日就已帶隊到大灣區考察，直至21日才結束行程。根據政府新聞處紀錄，下午6時左右才在珠海見完傳媒，總結大灣區考察之旅。然後他當晚就回到特首辦公室，在10時45分在文件上作出第一項修改－加入定義基本法第47條，要求特首就任時申報財產的原意。<br />\n<br />\n整份修訂建議分為三部分，分別為協議背景和性質、基本法第47條，以及利益衝突部分。梁振英首先處理了基本法第47條部分，只花了10分鐘就完成該部分多項修訂。<br />\n<br />\n之後他稍微修改了第三部分，再回到第一部分，即協議背景和性質，他首先就加入了「簽訂協議當日，是否已當選行政長官」的部分。其後再限制研究範圍，在澳洲傳媒公開的協議文本，隨後才補上真偽部分。<br />\n<br />\n他總共花了1小時17分鐘進行修訂，中途在11時33分至59分之間，曾停止了工作一段時間。"},{"pid":"bc738d903955fc4b168f66c2aec96bbbfdec7f23","tid":245850,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"做特首都好辛苦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b6afddd7f033ff9c235088ad7386f557938837","tid":245850,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T22:44:30.000Z","msg":"魔鬼在細節"},{"pid":"bc42bd4a0a63f811cfc61195c7590e33f5fbf18a","tid":245850,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T01:05:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94bba1d0aaaaa1f14541bf80b0a25878a79a42e7","tid":245850,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做特首都好辛苦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成世人都無講過一句真話就真係幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ef7677e8966307ebfc1199297d45d3bee8c2d6","tid":245850,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"大灣區有金盾，remote唔到返香港做野，要趕返來做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}